{"tid":464590,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超索香香透視騷胸 賀汪阿姐入行五十年","createTime":"2017-11-10T16:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T05:07:49.000Z","uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"24f670aaa0fa9d557da93f28d6704a642a410ae6","tid":464590,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"TVB今晚喺半島酒店搞咗個「汪明荃50周年世紀盛宴」，可以容納100位嘉賓，香港好多唔同界別嘅朋友都會嚟到，好似有藝員 、歌手、政府 官員、政界人士、慈善機構、粵劇界、文化界、唔同年代嘅合作同事等等，可謂賓客如雲。<br />\n<br />\n今晚有唔少藝人盛裝到場出席晚宴，好似新晉人妻岑麗香咁，身穿黑色連身繡花裙，心口有個大Deep V用黑色薄紗蓋住，事業線若隱若現，仲有一向出名夠潮嘅填詞人黃偉文，以一身粉紅色唐裝現身，仲有容祖兒晒腳、吊帶裝胡定欣等，夠晒搶眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000243_471a329e8051d40786664a69eef3cf18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000243_471a329e8051d40786664a69eef3cf18.jpg&h=3ef30975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000243_a6aef3c462bb605a0d5d152bea47de1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000243_a6aef3c462bb605a0d5d152bea47de1f.jpg&h=cb6c2043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000244_8ff5350fb91641c8a1580d95a84ff861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000244_8ff5350fb91641c8a1580d95a84ff861.jpg&h=65363943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000244_00ae94ac048f5870abc1b9500431bc6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000244_00ae94ac048f5870abc1b9500431bc6f.jpg&h=702d5dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000245_6df8d8cb58f12dfe3f5e40c16ceb0c5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000245_6df8d8cb58f12dfe3f5e40c16ceb0c5d.jpg&h=ee96a9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000245_f6ede2fabca8d2f368e336329ad0d327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000245_f6ede2fabca8d2f368e336329ad0d327.jpg&h=17b649f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000246_9b8a490ce1b35fa9e271915536f78a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000246_9b8a490ce1b35fa9e271915536f78a55.jpg&h=420bfa34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"243de16eedb6c33494ebb76e2d0a9b256e935aab","tid":464590,"uid":2889,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"why文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d06153516644f45d1884fecc0f211c3e3d4152a","tid":464590,"uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"阿姐一個月前約實 宣萱推Job都要到<br />\n<br />\nTVB今晚喺半島酒店搞咗個「汪明荃50周年世紀盛宴」，可以容納100位嘉賓，所以唔同界別嘅朋友都會嚟到，好似有藝員 、歌手 、政府 官員、政界人士、慈善機構、粵劇界、文化界、唔同年代嘅合作同事等等。<br />\n<br />\n阿姐今晚珠光寶氣，高貴優雅，佢笑笑口謂：「多謝贊助商啦，全部真嘢嚟0架！」但就謂不知價值多少。<br />\n<br />\n今晚賓客如雲，同樣都係台慶都未必請得動，阿姐話：「係呀，全部嘉賓都係我自己親自邀請，今晚主要都係同大家分享下，傾下之前合作嗰啲嘢呀，唱下歌傾下偈咁，比較warm嘅節目，Joey千嬅都會唱歌。」期待一陣會有乜嘢驚喜？阿姐話：「佢哋嚟已經好surprise，大家互相支持吖嘛，祖兒仲嚟咗我嘅排練室排添，好認真呀佢哋！佢唱我嘅歌唱得好好，你哋聽下。」<br />\n<br />\n宣萱都有出席呢個盛宴，佢話：「一個月前阿姐叫我出席，我就咩活動都推，就算賺錢嘅機會都會推，一定要出席。」宣萱又話曾經同過李克勤、阿姐係鄰居，曾試過食阿姐包雲吞同糭，試過有次家英哥唔記得帶鎖匙，企咗喺門口，宣萱就招呼家英哥上屋企坐。<br />\n<br />\n宣萱又話阿姐係佢嘅偶像，因為阿姐做嘢嘅時候好認真、準時，合作得好開心，不過私底下就係好搞笑，佢話：「試過同阿姐打麻將，點知阿姐贏好多，大家都怕咗同佢打牌。」佢又話阿姐係一個好好嘅榜樣，因為如果開工嘅時候阿姐喺度，就知道會好準時開工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/001610_27caabfd0282e9f6c94e2d0ec913d0e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F001610_27caabfd0282e9f6c94e2d0ec913d0e8.jpg&h=a667f1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/001611_5f1339a029a8c668fab68b0c377ba883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F001611_5f1339a029a8c668fab68b0c377ba883.jpg&h=2e83e6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/001611_92425cb169b216de51687c7122edc5dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F001611_92425cb169b216de51687c7122edc5dd.jpg&h=812cebc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7b2065b6e942f1116f00b97313ded2263cc079b","tid":464590,"uid":35504,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"上面咁多幅相阿姐嗰張最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93a02eabf510927c16fe1a9ac52e8b2aa3c217d","tid":464590,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好耐冇回帶過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea65dbcd8664aa9a08ffc47c7f3536ec4c1513b","tid":464590,"uid":100136,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/000245_f6ede2fabca8d2f368e336329ad0d327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F000245_f6ede2fabca8d2f368e336329ad0d327.jpg&h=17b649f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做乜柒呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d2c0c9e8ab23328e125bdf49470a8ca833ccc7","tid":464590,"uid":13187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:40