a8728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ujnargB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FujnargB.jpg&h=387babcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dJcobUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdJcobUx.jpg&h=8f0531c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿姐不時向觀眾展示長在其右邊白滑腋下肌膚的小痣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FbNodf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFbNodf5.jpg&h=64d69455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VVckxRX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVVckxRX.jpg&h=f642c3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bEN45yh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbEN45yh.jpg&h=ce00f29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 明言要&quot;push up&quot;自己既阿蛆夾出四吋洪溝，實在令人目不暇給，眼睛都唔知要望邊好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1YF5Tsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1YF5Tsf.jpg&h=c2d45d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿蛆不時拋出可愛雞蘿柚既姿態，教人垂涎三尺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rr21OS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Frr21OS6.jpg&h=34b7b92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿蛆不忘展示大腿柔軟度"},{"pid":"730e2df3c56ee710c285f91c5ba2584db1e0eed7","tid":464590,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揚言會不斷push up 自己既阿姐真係有跡可尋<br />\n阿姐早喺8年前既台慶已經破格求變, 訓身大跳濕身舞<br />\n為觀眾大派長者福利 讓大家睇到目瞪口呆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AiiROBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAiiROBU.jpg&h=d1ce3e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐先以一part 鋼管舞作熱身<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aHXJ2To.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaHXJ2To.jpg&h=219bf142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單人solo 濕身辣舞既阿姐正在蘊釀能旺, 準備施展渾身解素​<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/elC3NiN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FelC3NiN.jpg&h=b5c25ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐正式爆發潛能 水花四起 霸氣十足<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QhkkKLT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQhkkKLT.jpg&h=d8754bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐即使濕身仍面帶笑容, 非常專業<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dPaikZn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdPaikZn.jpg&h=9cab7955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n視后胡定欣當年都跟唔上阿姐既步伐<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cm7S5gi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fcm7S5gi.jpg&h=d2d62ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/M4csN3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM4csN3j.jpg&h=4c4fbd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tS2qzD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtS2qzD6.jpg&h=32ae1fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後阿姐擺出終極老江湖姿態作結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y2dJdRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY2dJdRH.jpg&h=1c3f2e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hfOkD5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhfOkD5c.jpg&h=1e276854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辣舞過後, 仍熱情俯身騷事業安撫眾人</span></span>"},{"pid":"62900e1e46dc69bdf0e20db126a6572407234fd5","tid":464590,"uid":24160,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:50:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿姐圈內外都不知魅力非凡幾受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"